<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Reset Your Password</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{background:#f0f2f5;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif}.wrapper{max-width:600px;margin:40px auto;background:#fff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}.header{background:#0d1f4f;padding:28px 40px;text-align:center}.header h1{color:#fff;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px}.body{padding:40px}.greeting{font-size:1rem;color:#0d1f4f;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px}.text{font-size:.92rem;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px}.otp-box{text-align:center;margin:28px 0}.otp-code{font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:10px;color:#0d1f4f;background:#f4f6fb;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 32px;display:inline-block}.otp-expire{font-size:.82rem;color:#999;margin-top:10px}.divider{height:1px;background:#eee;margin:28px 0}.warning-box{background:#fff8e1;border-left:4px solid #f5a623;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:20px}.warning-box p{font-size:.85rem;color:#856404;line-height:1.6}.footer{background:#f4f6fb;padding:24px 40px;text-align:center}.footer p{font-size:.8rem;color:#aaa;line-height:1.6}.footer a{color:#e8610a;text-decoration:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header"><h1>LOVELISTICS</h1></div>
    <div class="body">
        <p class="greeting">Hi <%= fullName %>,</p>
        <p class="text">
            We received a request to reset your password. Use the OTP below to proceed.
            This code is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <p class="otp-expire">Expires in 5 minutes</p>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <p>⚠️ <strong>Never share this code with anyone.</strong> LOVELISTICS will never ask for your OTP via phone or chat.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="text" style="font-size:.82rem;">
            If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
            Your password will not be changed.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@lovelistics.com">support@lovelistics.com</a><br/>© 2026 LOVELISTICS. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>